nodes.title: Chat_Message _O (the init message)
widgets_values: act as prompt generator ,i will give you text and you describe an image that match that text in details, answer with one response only

updates
 - no longer need to use String nodes, so this new one is using 
   normal text parameter, so it is now compatible with other comfyUI 
   nodes that receive text

 - support selecting the model in chat Completion node
   so if you have access to gpt-4 you can use it

//note: using ChatGPT with revAnimated or mistoonAnime checkpoints produce stunning accurate results

updates
 - create image input now is text instead of string, so it can be
   Compatible with any other text nodes 
 - also add fake seeds to force the node to generate new input each 
   cycle if needed

updates
 - remove the no longer necessary string node 
 - add new NSP node
 - enhanced the text2image node

updates
 - this node will select a random value from the NSP file included 
   with the Package based on the terminology you select

- combine two text inputs to one text also 
   it will add the separator in the middle

- replaces all occurrences of (old) with 
   the new) value

- debug will write text to the 
   console screen

- use text instead of String
 - allow transparent text and BG
 - allow you to set image size
 - expand: this option will resize the 
           result image to fit the text if 
           the image don't fit 
 - x,y is to move the text around the image 
       it points to text center

- trim removes any extra spaces after or 
   before the text if found
